(17, 25, '23060922ehc_page.jpg', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Welcome to Executive Health Clinic, where your health is our priority. Our team of experienced consultants is dedicated to providing personalized care tailored to your unique needs. With cutting-edge facilities and state-of-the-art technology, we offer advanced screening tests to ensure comprehensive health assessments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">At Executive Health Clinic, we understand that every individual is different. That&#39;s why we offer tailored screening packages designed to meet diverse needs and lifestyles. Whether you&#39;re looking for a basic check-up or a more comprehensive assessment, we have a package that&#39;s right for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Our core focus is on early detection and prevention. By identifying potential health risks early on, we can help you take proactive steps to maintain your health and well-being. Our screening packages are designed to catch issues before they become serious, giving you peace of mind and confidence in your health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">With Executive Health Clinic, you can expect compassionate care, advanced technology, and a commitment to your overall wellness. Take control of your health today and schedule your screening with us. Your journey to a healthier tomorrow starts here.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" style=\"border:0px solid black; height:600px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; width:1600px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" style=\"border:0px solid black; height:600px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-top:0px; width:1600px\" /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);

